"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-07-24-paris-drug-dealers-say-theyre-ready-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS, France (AFP) - France has declared itself prepared for the deluge of Olympics visitors - and so have Paris's drug dealers.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.6316937355954816, \"rank\": 0.4873321348389497, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}, {\"begin\": 22, \"end\": 28, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.6316937355954816, \"rank\": 0.4873321348389497, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}, {\"begin\": 108, \"end\": 113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999868578, \"rank\": 1.31335631496624e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The dealers have promised a steady supply of wares, but warned prices may go up and delivery wait times too under the weight of tens of thousands of security forces and heavy demand.\", \"from\": 131, \"to\": 313, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"From Parisians renting out their apartments, to a transit system that has boosted its ticket prices, everyone is looking to make a buck during the Games - and that includes the underworld.\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 503, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are always ready in this business,\\\" a Parisian dealer told AFP, echoing French leader Emmanuel Macron's judgment this week that his nation is all set for the Games.\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 673, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 568, \"end\": 571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9980425246882292, \"rank\": 0.001961314536318221, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}, {\"begin\": 581, \"end\": 587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.654306833465414, \"rank\": 0.34110567003927295, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}, {\"begin\": 595, \"end\": 610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There will always be somebody ready, that's how it is when there is money to be made,\\\" said the dealer, on condition of anonymity.\", \"from\": 675, \"to\": 806, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With up to 45,000 security forces policing the streets, experts expect delivery services will see a bump in clients seeking to avoid getting busted.\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 956, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, France has already had a boom in messaging app and social media-driven drug deliveries since pandemic lockdowns pushed the trade off the street and onto smartphone screens.\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 1139, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 967, \"end\": 973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.6316937355954816, \"rank\": 0.4873321348389497, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the same time, the country has voiced increasing alarm over a flourishing drug trade and deadly violence between rival gangs.\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1269, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a kind of Uberisation of drug trafficking, with the development of digital offerings on applications like Telegram, or promotional deals,\\\" said criminal attorney Adrien Gabeaud.\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1458, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1387, \"end\": 1395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telegraphy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.65518574381941e-21, \"text\": \"Telegram\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telegraphy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telegraphy\"}, {\"begin\": 1443, \"end\": 1449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Adrien\", \"score\": 0.999999999794909, \"rank\": 1.0010462649987534e-10, \"text\": \"Adrien\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Adrien\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Adrien\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the run-up to the Games, dealers have been updating their clients on feeds with what to expect during the competition that opens Friday and runs through August 11.\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1626, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The prices of our services will be adjusted due to challenging road traffic conditions and heavy demand,\\\" one seller wrote to customers.\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1765, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Swathes of central Paris are blocked off during the festivities, snarling car and pedestrian traffic enough that the Parisian dealer said it would not be worth the trouble, even to see the events.\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1963, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1786, \"end\": 1791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999868578, \"rank\": 1.31335631496624e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In one exchange between a seller and customer, seen by AFP, the dealer warns that transactions cannot happen in the open.\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 2086, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2020, \"end\": 2023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9980425246882292, \"rank\": 0.001961314536318221, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The police are on the lookout,\\\" the message read.\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2138, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet other dealers are sending out messages to assure clients, like one that wrote: \\\"I inform you that despite the Olympics, the delivery service will remain the same.\\\"\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2307, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's too soon to gauge whether or how much prices could rise, but criminal lawyer David Curiel predicted they are on their way up.\", \"from\": 2309, \"to\": 2439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2391, \"end\": 2403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Curiel\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Curiel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Curiel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Curiel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In Paris a gram of cocaine costs 50-60 euros ($55-65), but now it could probably go up to 80 euros a gram,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2441, \"to\": 2558, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2445, \"end\": 2450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999868578, \"rank\": 1.31335631496624e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They (dealers) can not wait, for them this is like the sales,\\\" he added, referring to France's government-set promotion periods when shoppers flock to stores.\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2647, \"end\": 2653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.6316937355954816, \"rank\": 0.4873321348389497, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France has pledged to crack down on digital drug sales and has deployed massive amounts of police to patrol Paris during the Games that are expected to attract 15 million people.\", \"from\": 2721, \"to\": 2899, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2721, \"end\": 2727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.6316937355954816, \"rank\": 0.4873321348389497, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}, {\"begin\": 2829, \"end\": 2834, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999868578, \"rank\": 1.31335631496624e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But will there be a boom?\", \"from\": 2901, \"to\": 2926, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"An AFP check of drug sales prices advertised on messaging apps did not reveal an immediate spike, and police sources were also sceptical.\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 3065, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2931, \"end\": 2934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9980425246882292, \"rank\": 0.001961314536318221, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"No 'Olympics effect' so far\\\" on boosting drug sales, a narcotics investigator told AFP, again on condition of anonymity.\", \"from\": 3067, \"to\": 3188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3151, \"end\": 3154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9980425246882292, \"rank\": 0.001961314536318221, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is already an incredible amount (of drugs) on offer,\\\" the investigator noted.\", \"from\": 3190, \"to\": 3274, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On that much, the police and dealers seem to agree.\", \"from\": 3276, \"to\": 3327, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"During Covid it was different.\", \"from\": 3329, \"to\": 3360, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There was an incredible spike in prices, by two or three times.\", \"from\": 3361, \"to\": 3424, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a fight to find anything,\\\" the Parisian dealer said.\", \"from\": 3425, \"to\": 3484, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been fine ahead of the Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 3485, \"to\": 3524, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The real effect on Paris's -- and France's -- drug market will not become clear immediately but researchers have begun pondering the impact.\", \"from\": 3526, \"to\": 3666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3545, \"end\": 3550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999868578, \"rank\": 1.31335631496624e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3560, \"end\": 3566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.6316937355954816, \"rank\": 0.4873321348389497, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Law enforcement is heavily mobilised for the Olympics, but is that going to give (dealers) more opportunity to pursue their business elsewhere in France?\\\"\", \"from\": 3668, \"to\": 3823, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3815, \"end\": 3821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.6316937355954816, \"rank\": 0.4873321348389497, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"asked economist Nacer Lalam.\", \"from\": 3824, \"to\": 3852, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3846, \"end\": 3851, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lalam,_Kottayam\", \"score\": 0.669467902590356, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lalam\", \"types\": [\"Q532\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lalam,_Kottayam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lalam,_Kottayam\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That will be something we will not know until after the fact.\\\"\", \"from\": 3854, \"to\": 3917, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tags:  HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 3919, \"to\": 3937, \"entities\": []}]}"